---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import contact from '../data/contact.json';

const { email } = contact;
const mailtoHref = `mailto:${email}`;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Saramonse Beauty"
  description="Sara Monse Beauty — how we use and protect your information."
  scrollCompactNav={true}
>
  <!-- Hero title: vector (responsive width; matches About / FAQ / Contact) -->
  <section class="pt-6 sm:pt-8 lg:pt-10 pb-12 sm:pb-16 lg:pb-20 px-6 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex justify-center">
      <h1 class="w-[88%] sm:w-[72%] md:w-[58%] lg:w-[45%] max-w-full shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/assets/privacy-policy-title.svg"
          alt="Privacy Policy"
          class="block w-full h-auto mx-auto"
          width="2048"
          height="589"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-16 sm:pb-20 lg:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans tracking-wide mb-10 sm:mb-12">Last updated: 5 April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 sm:space-y-12 lg:space-y-14">
        <section class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            This privacy policy explains how Sara Monse Beauty uses and protects any information that you provide when
            booking with us, visiting our website, or engaging with us on social media.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            We are committed to treating your personal information responsibly and ensuring that your privacy is
            protected. Should we ask you to provide certain information by which you can be identified, you can be
            assured that it will only be used in accordance with this privacy statement.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            We may update this policy from time to time. Please check this page regularly to ensure you are happy with any
            changes. It is also your responsibility to keep your client profile details up to date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            What We Collect
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We may collect the following information when you book via our booking system (Fresha), update your profile,
            or communicate with us directly:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Your date of birth</li>
            <li>Contact information such as your email address, telephone number, and (if applicable) address</li>
            <li>
              Payment details (taken securely via Fresha’s third-party payment processor – Sara Monse Beauty does not
              store card details)
            </li>
            <li>Relevant information for consultations, aftercare, or treatment suitability (e.g., allergies, medical conditions)</li>
            <li>Other information you choose to share with us (e.g., surveys, preferences, or feedback)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            How We Use This Information
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mb-4">We collect and use this information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>Manage and improve our treatments and services</li>
            <li>Personalise your experience with us</li>
            <li>Verify your identity for bookings</li>
            <li>Keep internal records (appointments, payments, treatment notes)</li>
            <li>Send appointment confirmations, reminders, or important updates</li>
            <li>
              With your consent, send promotional offers, seasonal news, or updates about Sara Monse Beauty (you can
              unsubscribe at any time)
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mt-6">
            We will only disclose your information if required by law or in response to lawful requests by public
            authorities.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Lawful Bases for Processing
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Under the UK GDPR, we rely on the following lawful bases:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-3 text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Contract</strong> – processing is necessary to provide the treatments and services you have booked.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Legal obligation</strong> – keeping certain treatment notes and records for insurance or HMRC requirements.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Legitimate interests</strong> – using your details for appointment management and communication.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Consent</strong> – sending you marketing communications. You can withdraw consent at any time.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Data Retention
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mb-4">We keep personal data only for as long as necessary:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-3 text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>
              Treatment &amp; consultation notes – retained for 7 years (or, for clients under 18, until age 25) in line
              with insurance and legal requirements.
            </li>
            <li>
              Booking &amp; contact details – kept while you remain an active client. If you have not booked with us for 2
              years, we will securely delete your records.
            </li>
            <li>Marketing consent – kept until you unsubscribe or withdraw consent.</li>
            <li>
              Payment details – never stored by Sara Monse Beauty. Payments are processed securely via Fresha’s
              third-party system.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Security
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            We are committed to keeping your information safe. Fresha provides secure online booking and payment
            processing. We also have appropriate physical, electronic, and managerial measures in place to protect your
            information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Our website may use cookies (small files stored on your device) to improve your browsing experience and help
            us understand how visitors use our site. You can choose to accept or decline cookies in your browser
            settings. Please note that disabling cookies may limit some website functionality.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Links to Other Websites
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Our website or social media may contain links to other websites of interest. Once you leave our site, please
            note we have no control over external websites, and this privacy policy no longer applies. Always check the
            privacy statement of any website you visit.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Your Rights
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mb-4">Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of any inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
            <li>Request erasure of your data (“the right to be forgotten”) where legally possible</li>
            <li>Restrict or object to processing in certain circumstances</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for marketing at any time</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 sm:mb-8"
            style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;"
          >
            Contact Us
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mb-4">For privacy-related requests, please contact us at:</p>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
            <a
              href={mailtoHref}
              class="text-gray-900 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-gray-400 transition-opacity hover:opacity-80"
              >{email}</a
            >
          </p>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 font-sans leading-relaxed mt-6">We aim to respond to all requests within 30 days.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
